'''硼球烯'''（B<sub>40</sub>，Borospherene），是一個含有40個[[硼|硼]]原子的团簇分子。硼球烯與[[C60|C<sub>60</sub>]]相似，同為元素的球形結構<ref name=brown>{{cite web
|last1= Stacey
|first1= Kevin
|title= Researchers discover boron "buckyball"
|url= https://news.brown.edu/articles/2014/07/buckyball
|website= <news.brown.edu>
|publisher= Brown University
|accessdate= 14 July 2014
|archive-date= 2015-01-16
|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150116183043/https://news.brown.edu/articles/2014/07/buckyball
|dead-url= no
}}</ref>，但具有不同的對稱性。[[王来生|王来生]]研究组發現了硼球烯，并在2014年7月的 [[自然化學雜誌|''Nature Chemistry'']] 上發表<ref name=nature>{{Cite journal
|doi = 10.1038/nchem.1999 |issn = 1755-4349 |volume = advance online publication
|last = Zhai |first = Hua-Jin |coauthors = Ya-Fan Zhao, Wei-Li Li, Qiang Chen, Hui Bai, Han-Shi Hu, Zachary A. Piazza, Wen-Juan Tian, Hai-Gang Lu, Yan-Bo Wu, Yue-Wen Mu, Guang-Feng Wei, Zhi-Pan Liu, Jun Li, Si-Dian Li, Lai-Sheng Wang
|title = Observation of an all-boron fullerene |journal = Nature Chemistry |accessdate = 2014-07-14 |date = 2014-07-13
|url = http://www.nature.com/nchem/journal/vaop/ncurrent/full/nchem.1999.html
}}</ref>了相关内容。硼球烯是近年来的一系列团簇分子，包括[[C60|C<sub>60</sub>]]、[[锡球烯|锡球烯]]（stannaspherene）以及[[铅球烯|铅球烯]]（plumbaspherene），中的最新发现的成员<ref name=stanna>{{Cite journal
|last = Cui |first = Li-Feng |coauthors = Xin Huang, Lei-Ming Wang, Dmitry Yu. Zubarev, Alexander I. Boldyrev, Jun Li, Lai-Sheng Wang
